HEADWORD: Truth-teller
<hw>Truth"-tell`er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who tells
the truth.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Truth-teller</qex> was our England's Alfred named.</q>
